{"tid":505040,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"公司抽奬中咗部 switch mario 主機套裝（有意較平出售","createTime":"2017-12-20T16:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T07:49:43.000Z","uid":133333,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a4d06aad95cc9de5a47b5ca746040d8a5e22c1","tid":505040,"uid":133333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/004232_990f3c7b5fb5df5de787c953b77d5056.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F004232_990f3c7b5fb5df5de787c953b77d5056.jpg&h=f329accb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/004233_3513170f6df32fb95576f88b115059ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F004233_3513170f6df32fb95576f88b115059ea.jpg&h=6005938c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n物品詳情：<a href=\"https://m.price.com.hk/product.php?p=278573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.price.com.hk%2Fproduct.php%3Fp%3D278573&d=DNPXVaOhVSc17oZzA7E6%2F8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=66491237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.price.com.hk/product.php?p=278573</a><br />\n<br />\n事緣<br />\n<br />\n小弟公司前日聖誕抽奬 抽中左上圖主機<br />\n可惜小弟平日唔打機 所以得物無所用<br />\n<br />\n可惜因為公司聖誕抽奬 冇購買收據<br />\n小弟公司在香港都算有頭有面 應該唔會買水貨<br />\n<br />\n明白冇收據係會難做啲 所以有意較平出售<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打 買返去做聖誕禮物<br />\n送比朋友屋企人情人都好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有意TG:  <a href=\"https://t.me/S0911027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FS0911027&d=DNPXVaOhVSc17oZzA7E6%2F8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f3271c8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/S0911027</a>"},{"pid":"17310a7236bbc8a51820bd7952450b0d0a1